<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3467956>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Phoberus ntlenyanae Strümpher, new species, holotype. 1, dorsal habitus; 2, lateral habitus; 3, dorsal and lateral views of aedeagus; 4, holotype labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3467956/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3467958>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–8. Lectotype of Trox caffer Harold, 1872, designated by Scholtz 1980: 95 (MNHN). 5, dorsal habitus; 6, lateral habitus; 7, dorsal and lateral views of aedeagus; 8, lectotype labels. Photographs by Antoine Mantilleri, copyright MNHN." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3467958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3467960>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Phoberus caffer (Harold, 1872), specimen with indument removed (TMSA). 9, dorsal habitus; 10, lateral habitus; 11, dorsal and lateral views of aedeagus 12, labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3467960/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3467964>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–18. Phoberus lilianae (Scholtz, 1980), paratype (SAMC). 14, dorsal habitus; 15, lateral habitus; 16, dorsal and lateral views of aedeagus; 17, paratype labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3467964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

